#### 📄 [repository/UserRepository.kt](file:///d:/Tugas%20pak%20isna/MenuKita/app/src/main/java/com/example/menukita/repository/UserRepository.kt) — Login & Register

```kotlin
class UserRepository {
    private val db = FirebaseDatabase.getInstance("https://menukita-feb11-default-rtdb.asia-southeast1.firebasedatabase.app")
    private val userRef = db.getReference("users")
```

**Fungsi-fungsi:**

| Fungsi | Penjelasan |
|--------|------------|
| [register()](file:///d:/Tugas%20pak%20isna/MenuKita/app/src/main/java/com/example/menukita/repository/UserRepository.kt#15-51) | Mendaftarkan user baru. **Cek duplikasi email** dulu sebelum menyimpan. Key di Firebase = email yang dimodifikasi (`.` → `_`, `@` → `_at_`) |
| [login()](file:///d:/Tugas%20pak%20isna/MenuKita/app/src/main/java/com/example/menukita/repository/UserRepository.kt#52-75) | Mencari user berdasarkan email menggunakan `orderByChild("email").equalTo(email)`. Jika ditemukan, kembalikan objek [User](file:///d:/Tugas%20pak%20isna/MenuKita/app/src/main/java/com/example/menukita/model/User.kt#3-11) |

**Detail Register:**
```kotlin
fun register(user: User, onComplete: (Boolean, String?) -> Unit) {
    // 1. Cek email kosong atau tidak
    // 2. Query: apakah email sudah terdaftar?
    userRef.orderByChild("email").equalTo(email)
        .addListenerForSingleValueEvent(object : ValueEventListener {
            override fun onDataChange(snapshot: DataSnapshot) {
                if (snapshot.exists()) {
                    onComplete(false, "Email sudah terdaftar!")
                } else {
                    // 3. Simpan user baru ke Firebase
                    val emailKey = email.replace(".", "_").replace("@", "_at_")
                    userRef.child(emailKey).setValue(user)
                }
            }
        })
}
```

**Detail Login:**
```kotlin
fun login(email: String, onComplete: (User?, String?) -> Unit) {
    userRef.orderByChild("email").equalTo(email)
        .addListenerForSingleValueEvent(object : ValueEventListener {
            override fun onDataChange(snapshot: DataSnapshot) {
                if (snapshot.exists()) {
                    val user = snapshot.children.first().getValue(User::class.java)
                    onComplete(user, null) // User ditemukan
                } else {
                    onComplete(null, "Akun tidak ditemukan")
                }
            }
        })
}
```

