```

**Perbedaan dengan MenuAdapter:**
| Aspek | MenuAdapter | MenuGridAdapter |
|-------|-------------|-----------------|
| Layout | [item_menu.xml](file:///d:/Tugas%20pak%20isna/MenuKita/app/src/main/res/layout/item_menu.xml) (horizontal card) | [item_menu_grid.xml](file:///d:/Tugas%20pak%20isna/MenuKita/app/src/main/res/layout/item_menu_grid.xml) (vertikal card) |
| Tampilan | List 1 kolom | Grid 2 kolom |
| Dipakai di | [MainActivity](file:///d:/Tugas%20pak%20isna/MenuKita/app/src/main/java/com/example/menukita/MainActivity.kt#14-224) (Admin) | [UserDashboardActivity](file:///d:/Tugas%20pak%20isna/MenuKita/app/src/main/java/com/example/menukita/UserDashboardActivity.kt#14-111) (User) |
| LayoutManager | `LinearLayoutManager` | `GridLayoutManager(context, 2)` |

