## 5. Alur Aplikasi

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Buka Aplikasi] --> B[LoginActivity]
    B --> C{Sudah punya akun?}
    C -->|Belum| D[RegisterActivity]
    D --> B
    C -->|Sudah| E[Input Email + Password]
    E --> F{Login berhasil?}
    F -->|Gagal| B
    F -->|Berhasil| G{Cek Role}
    G -->|Admin| H[MainActivity - Dashboard Admin]
    G -->|User| I[UserDashboardActivity - Dashboard User]
    
    H --> J[Lihat Daftar Menu - List View]
    H --> K[Tambah Menu - AddMenuActivity]
    H --> L[Edit/Hapus Menu - EditMenuActivity]
    H --> M[Search & Filter & Sort]
    H --> N[ProfileActivity - Logout]
    
    I --> O[Lihat Daftar Menu - Grid View]
    I --> P[Search & Filter]
    I --> Q[ProfileActivity - Logout]
    
    N --> B
    Q --> B
```

